{"tid":2176560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我同我媽嘅對話","createTime":"2020-08-27T07:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T07:31:42.000Z","uid":318634,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3a63bba682990ea58f07c75215c85c53afd8c0f7","tid":2176560,"uid":318634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:25:37.000Z","msg":"👩🏻&zwj;🦰:呀仔啊做咩電視成日講呢個女仔嘅死？<br />\n<br />\n🧑🏻&zwj;🦲:之前呢有個女仔游水好叻，但除曬衫跳海「自殺」<br />\n<br />\n👩🏻&zwj;🦰:游水好叻但跳海自殺？好唔合理喎，仲要除曬衫，冇一個女仔會願意落到去冇衫着<br />\n<br />\n🧑🏻&zwj;🦲:事實心水清都知，發現左一日都唔夠就火化<br />\n<br />\n👩🏻&zwj;🦰:正常人死左都要排隊排幾日先火化，仲唔叫有鬼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我老母六十幾歲盲字都唔識多隻都知道有鬼<br />\n陪審團唔係唔明？<br />\n<br />\n對家係咁話精神有問題<br />\n但係要記住<br />\n<br />\n一個熟水性嘅人<br />\n用最蠢嘅方法死？<br />\n呢個最侮辱自己嘅死法"},{"pid":"d29ae7c876e22e2db6cf7fafdd9d9ff8b147a35b","tid":2176560,"uid":318634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:25:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3f83a019aaab87ac4ca9296bb71d89bcb0032c0","tid":2176560,"uid":318634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:26:11.000Z","msg":"推比陪審團睇"},{"pid":"23113db6736eb5ea97da25318913109b359deccd","tid":2176560,"uid":29929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:27:51.000Z","msg":"球證 旁證 足協 足總都係我嘅人jpg"},{"pid":"255241844cc3c40d9893eb6f0a4b0f0300e0087d","tid":2176560,"uid":318634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23113db6736eb5ea97da25318913109b359deccd","tid":2176560,"uid":29929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:27:51.000Z","msg":"球證 旁證 足協 足總都係我嘅人jpg"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:29:18.000Z","msg":"其實我好奇香港仲有幾多人唔知呢個事情真相"},{"pid":"4f515b160e43120ab762c941d4d06b87a9cf115f","tid":2176560,"uid":318634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:31:42.000Z","msg":"唔同意嘅人講下<br />\n睇下我點反駁"}]}